    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">K-Electric Customer Service</h2>
    <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">K-Electric offers multiple complaint channels for billing disputes, power outages, and new connections:</p>
    <ul class="space-y-2 text-neutral-600 mb-6 list-disc list-inside">
      <li><strong>Central helpline:</strong> 118 (toll-free from Karachi) or 021-99000000 from mobile</li>
      <li><strong>Billing disputes:</strong> 021-99008200</li>
      <li><strong>WhatsApp complaints:</strong> 0348-0000118 (official K-Electric number)</li>
      <li><strong>Online complaint:</strong> ke.com.pk → "Customer Services" → "Register Complaint"</li>
      <li><strong>Email:</strong> info@ke.com.pk</li>
      <li><strong>Customer service centers:</strong> I.I. Chundrigar Road HQ, Clifton, Gulshan, North Nazimabad, Korangi, Malir, Bahadurabad, Federal B Area</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-2xl font-heading font-bold mt-8 mb-4">Tips for K-Electric Consumers</h2>
    <ul class="space-y-3 text-neutral-600 mb-6 list-disc list-inside">
      <li><strong>Save your 13-digit account number</strong> in your phone's notes — saves time every month.</li>
      <li><strong>Pay 3–5 days before due date</strong> — K-Electric disconnects very promptly after due date.</li>
      <li><strong>Stay under 200 units</strong> to qualify for Protected Consumer subsidy (30–40% discount).</li>
      <li><strong>Report power outages immediately</strong> via WhatsApp 0348-0000118 — K-Electric tracks response times.</li>
      <li><strong>For new connections</strong>, apply at K-Electric CSC with CNIC + ownership/tenancy documents. Connection fee: Rs. 4,500–6,500 for domestic single-phase. Timeline: 30–45 days.</li>
      <li><strong>Check for "slab protection"</strong> on your bill — K-Electric offers slab protection for consumers who consistently use less than 200 units.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-bold text-neutral-900 mt-8 mb-4">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
    <div class="space-y-3 mb-10">
      <details class="faq-item"><summary class="faq-question">How to check K-Electric bill online?</summary><div class="px-4 pb-4 text-sm text-neutral-600">Go to pakistanbill.online/k-electric-bill/ and enter your 13-digit K-Electric account number. Your Karachi electricity bill loads instantly — free, no login, no app required.</div></details>
